$ R: connection class to access external data
@ connection

→ development/languages/R can access external data (such as data in Excel, databases, csv files etc.) through the *connection* class.

An object whose type is connection might be created with
→ development/languages/R/functions/stdin[`stdin()`], `stdout` or `stderr()`:
gh|about-r|/classes/connection/create-connection.R||

sa:

  → development/languages/R/tasks/import-data-into-R-for-processing

  → development/languages/R/functions/textConnection[`textConnection()`]

  → development/languages/R/classes
